All Implemented Interfaces:
DataTracker<SpaceData,​Metadata>, SimulationTracker, fr.cnrs.iees.rvgrid.observer.Observable<DataReceiver<SpaceData,​Metadata>>, fr.cnrs.iees.rvgrid.observer.Observer, fr.cnrs.iees.rvgrid.rendezvous.GridNode, fr.ens.biologie.generic.Resettable, fr.ens.biologie.generic.Singleton<Metadata>
public class SpaceDataTracker extends AbstractDataTracker<SpaceData,​Metadata>

A data tracker for spatial data. It sends change data to whoever is listening (usually a Widget understanding SpaceData messages). Messages consist in a time stamp and a list of changes to the previous state of the space (deletion/creation/move of points and lines).

The metadata are the space properties, namely:

  • type (SpaceType),
  • edgeEffects (EdgeEffects),
  • precision (double),
  • units (String),

plus the descendant-specific properties:

  • for FlatSurface:
    • x-limits (Interval) and
    • y-limits (Interval)
  • for SquareGrid:
    • cellSize(double),
    • x-nCells (int),
    • y-nCells (int) (optional, if absent = x-nCells)

This DataTracker is not instantiated by a DataTrackerNode, but by the SpaceNode it points to.
